    "Weight initialization initializes the weights of the neural network's connections to appropriate values to prevent vanishing or exploding gradients during training and accelerate convergence.",
    "What is the role of learning rate scheduling in deep learning?",
    "Learning rate scheduling dynamically adjusts the learning rate during training to improve convergence and stability, allowing the model to navigate the optimization landscape more effectively.",
    "What is the difference between online learning and batch learning?",
    "In online learning, the model is updated incrementally after processing each individual data point, while in batch learning, the model is updated after processing a fixed-size batch of data samples.",
